{"tid":1727244,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"解放軍違憲出動，有無人申請司法覆核/臨時禁制令","createTime":"2019-11-16T11:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T11:36:56.000Z","uid":138409,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a123479371cab25bfa365c5b2edb6589ce73f94a","tid":1727244,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"之前連登禁制令單嘢都有人覆核<br />\n依家唔係唔覆核啊嘛？<br />\n<br />\n點樣違憲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lawlaydream/photos/a.625475004302516/1246711675512176/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flawlaydream%2Fphotos%2Fa.625475004302516%2F1246711675512176%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=35ecac5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lawlaydream/photos/a.625475004302516/1246711675512176/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n疑問回答<br />\nQ：屌，就係要解放軍出動攬炒啊嘛，做咩阻止佢哋呢？<br />\nA：解放軍出動攬炒嘅條件，係講緊解放軍出兵過程好難睇，嚴重違反民意、流血鎮壓市民之類，動搖香港自治地位，先有可能令美國感覺到有迫切需要取消對香港嘅優惠待遇；依家中共擺明想試探民意，溫水煮蛙，令解放軍出動恆常化，形造一種「出兵都無乜大不了啦」嘅感覺。<span style=\"color: gold;\">等啲外國政府習以為常到時，就算你想攬炒都炒唔到。</span><br />\n<br />\nQ：有無勝算？<br />\nA：問過法夢比卡超，佢話唔知，因為根本唔知法院響呢樣嘢上有無司法管轄權，但可以一試；暫時亦都無相關案例可作參考，因為唔知依家解放軍嘅行動算唔算「國家行為」<br />\n<br />\n求各位推上去<br />\n畀啲搞開法律戰線嘅人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f191df45a3cc968c5ddd2bbca6e3a9b21b64b6","tid":1727244,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f2d5c432ad6621640a32c54218f11ee7318c4c9c","tid":1727244,"uid":276839,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"快啲幫我做, 我冇錢冇人,唔該."},{"pid":"238a0822d182a7ac1c3409cc83a9216216badfdf","tid":1727244,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6943da1e5963bed372154d6e8abcabfb007932db","tid":1727244,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:34:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"21911e7258de52c23eb5fb9abda94fba46700fe8","tid":1727244,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"有眾籌我支持"},{"pid":"91b13bea17c5cb0bf215f92b60f96e5ab2f4c35a","tid":1727244,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c4e3dafe2c4ef55a022b69fd39850604f50a2d5","tid":1727244,"uid":277578,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:36:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得解放軍好過黑警<br />\n至少識摺被<br />\n黑警又唔讀書，又唔做野。"},{"pid":"14247835a7338784061de3e1b7ba529cc61684d5","tid":1727244,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"呢件事沈默嘅 都係簡接 接受中共統治 接受人治<br />\n<br />\n香港有咩事 全部都係幫兇"},{"pid":"c56fcf596622c396506a406034b546fc6497b23b","tid":1727244,"uid":1524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d8d2791035f0add0199fc832ad55b0d3410a62","tid":1727244,"uid":282359,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:42:49.000Z","msg":"又話法治已死但係成日走去JR/禁制令。精神分裂乎？<br />\n<br />\n你係要推翻個制度就唔好做埋啲無謂嘢。<br />\n又話唔信個制度但係一有起事就用個制度救命，咁你食屎啦。<br />\n就同啲成日屌黨鐵壞車但係就日日搭嘅豬一樣。"},{"pid":"9f87cfe61f7e892f59a07e5e8f6638d5399e4a84","tid":1727244,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:43:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6edb0b716354f764d2ecf2d02f2b8082bc3a9d4c","tid":1727244,"uid":138409,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c4e3dafe2c4ef55a022b69fd39850604f50a2d5","tid":1727244,"uid":277578,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:36:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得解放軍好過黑警<br />\n至少識摺被<br />\n黑警又唔讀書，又唔做野